  "detailed_description": "The goal of the game is to collect 22 bills. To collect them, you need to press the \"play\" button and move to the sandbox level.<br>[center] <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438020/extras/e93f23e73715bc2b1c239e44484bb5a3.poster.avif?t=1701314375\" width=320 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438020/extras/e93f23e73715bc2b1c239e44484bb5a3.webm?t=1701314375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438020/extras/e93f23e73715bc2b1c239e44484bb5a3.mp4?t=1701314375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>[/center]<br>On the level just remove the sand and lower the figure of the girl below, on the rocks (careful, if you touch the top or bottom frame, the level will end).<br><br>A new note is obtained only if the girl figure has reached the rocks below.<br><br>Inside the bag phone, notepad and water.<br><br>In the notebook you can pump traction (manually or auto), glow, the visibility of coins and the value of the level.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438020/extras/b9980205bf0293f8f9084f0d03f8503d.poster.avif?t=1701314375\" width=320 height=323 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438020/extras/b9980205bf0293f8f9084f0d03f8503d.webm?t=1701314375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Enhancements are bought with coins collected on the level.<br><br>Features:<br>- pleasant graphics;<br>- simple controls;<br>- interesting gameplay;",
